      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KINGSBRAE MAGGIE (1) has a strong record this track and trip with five wins and six placings from 15 starts. Placed last time (17.86) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 5.5 lengths. Has the ability and should feature. QUIRKY NACHO (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (17.58) at this track behind True Blue Billy in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Can measure up. TRALEE NADIA (5) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 0.8 lengths away in second (17.68) behind Canya Negotiate at this track. Will give a great sight again. SHE'S SEEKING (6) missed the frame latest (17.98) when fourth over 300m at this track in a Grade 4. Already a winner from this draw.",
